<h1>Mervi Emilia</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://merviemilia.com/now">merviemilia.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Helsinki

Finland
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Freelance artist and designer
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I make websites and brands, create art and illustrations, do online marketing, and write.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I cannot stop creating, and I enjoy freedom, autonomy and variation in what I do. I thrive on beauty and doing things right and well. The web works for me as a platform for it all.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
It is quite okay to be untitled, undefined and uncategorised. Niches may be commercial successes, but the world also needs multitalented, renaissance people and dreamers.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
“A Whole New Mind” by Daniel H. Pink
</p>

